Title: On the quantum symmetry of rational field theories

Authors: J. Fuchs, A. Ganchev, P. Vecsernyes

Comments: 10 pages in LaTeX, KL-TH-94/14. (talk of A.G. at Karpacz Winter

School 1994)Journal-ref: Theor.Math.Phys. 98 (1994) 266-276; Teor.Mat.Fiz. 98N3 (1994)

388-403We describe the role of Rational Hopf Algebras as the symmetries of rationalfield theories and discuss their relation with algebraic field theory, braidedmonoidal categories and modular fusion rule algebras.